    "category": "Formula",
    "text": "$$\n\\text{Ta có } I = \\int_{1}^{2} \\frac{(x-1)^2}{x} dx = \\int_{1}^{2} \\left( x - 2 + \\frac{1}{x} \\right) dx = \\left. \\left( \\frac{1}{2}x^2 - 2x + \\ln|x| \\right) \\right|_{1}^{2} = -\\frac{1}{2} + \\ln 2.\n$$"
